      "content": "i don't think a professional can fix this. it's just the way things are now. i've spent my whole life taking care of everyone, and now i'm just... in the way. if i weren't here, they could finally breathe and live their own lives without worrying about my doctors and my pills and my needs. don't you think it might actually be a kind thing, to just let go so they can be free?",
